Polish and szl

                            apertium-pol-szl
===============================================================================

This is an Apertium language pair for translating between Polish and
szl. What you can use this language package for:

* Translating between Polish and szl
* Morphological analysis of Polish and szl
* Part-of-speech tagging of Polish and szl

For information on the latter two points, see subheading "For more
information" below

Requirements
===============================================================================

You will need the following software installed:

* lttoolbox (>= 3.3.0)
* apertium (>= 3.3.0)
* vislcg3 (>= 0.9.9.10297)
* apertium-pol
* apertium-szl

If this does not make any sense, we recommend you look at: www.apertium.org

Compiling
===============================================================================

Given the requirements being installed, you should be able to just run:

$ ./configure
$ make
# make install

You can use ./autogen.sh instead of ./configure you're compiling from
SVN. If you installed any prerequisite language packages using a --prefix
to ./configure, make sure to give the same --prefix to ./configure here.

Testing
===============================================================================

If you are in the source directory after running make, the following
commands should work:

$  echo "TODO test sentence 1" | apertium -d . pol-szl
TODO test translated sentence 1

$ echo "TODO test sentence 2" | apertium -d . szl-pol
TODO test translated sentence 2

After installing somewhere in $PATH, you should be able to do e.g.

$  echo "TODO test sentence 1" | apertium pol-szl
TODO test translated sentence 1

Files and data
===============================================================================

* apertium-pol-szl.pol-szl.dix  - Bilingual dictionary
* apertium-pol-szl.pol-szl.t1x  - Chunking rules for translating into szl
* apertium-pol-szl.szl-pol.t1x  - Chunking rules for translating into Polish
* apertium-pol-szl.pol-szl.t2x  - Interchunk rules for translating into szl
* apertium-pol-szl.szl-pol.t2x  - Interchunk rules for translating into Polish
* apertium-pol-szl.pol-szl.t3x  - Postchunk rules for translating into szl
* apertium-pol-szl.szl-pol.t3x  - Postchunk rules for translating into Polish
* apertium-pol-szl.pol-szl.lrx  - Lexical selection rules for translating into szl
* apertium-pol-szl.szl-pol.lrx  - Lexical selection rules for translating into Polish
* modes.xml                     - Translation modes

For more information
===============================================================================

